---
title: HelloHero: Crumbed Hoki & Veggie Couscous with Garlic Dip & Slivered Almonds
description: A golden and crunchy crumb on hoki is the only way to go. It matches the bright and sunny couscous, tossed with roast veggies and there’s a zap of zest in this bowl too. Everything is shining and golden tonight!

